  "description": {
   "en": "A man’s romantic dates with his boyfriend keep turning naughty. A shy teenage boy dreams of becoming a woman to fulfill his best friend’s fantasies. A farm boy in the big city winds up working as a gigolo—and then his innocent younger cousin shows up for a visit. A manga artist reluctantly takes a job drawing yaoi manga, only to find that his artwork reveals his hidden desires. This collection of unabashedly sensual short stories includes all these encounters and more.  \n  \nCertain stories in Perfect Training are sequels to stories in Danshi Meiro."
